Rousseff Says Brazil Needs to Keep Eyes on Inflation and Growth

-- B y   A n d r e   S o l i a n i
-- 
2011-10-13T20:13:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/rousseff-says-brazil-needs-to-keep-eyes-on-inflation-and-growth.html
Brazil  needs to keep one eye on
inflation, and one eye on growth, President  Dilma Rousseff  said.  The country must be “serious and prudent” in its
macroeconomic policies, Rousseff said today at an event in
Curitiba.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andre Soliani in Brasilia at 
